OL,3,CUN human rights expert warns Israel is
OL,4,Cinflicting 'wanton destruction' on Gaza
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,7,FNews, Francesca Albanese, the UN's
OL,8,FSpecial Rapporteur on the OPT, accused
OL,9,FIsrael of inflicting "starvation" on
OL,10,FPalestinians in Gaza.
OL,12,FThe UN has warned of imminent famine
OL,13,Fafter a month which saw aid levels
OL,14,Freach their lowest in 2024.
