OL,4,Cinflicting 'wanton destruction' on Gaza
OL,6,FIsrael has insisted there is a
OL,7,Fmilitary and moral justification for
OL,8,Feverything it does in Gaza, despite
OL,9,Fits military operation into the Gaza
OL,10,FStrip having now killed more than
OL,11,F43,000 people - many of them women and
OL,12,Fchildren.
