OL,3,CUN human rights expert warns Israel is
OL,4,Cinflicting 'wanton destruction' on Gaza
OL,6,FMs Albanese's comments come after she
OL,7,Faddressed the UN last week on her
OL,8,Flatest report investigating the human
OL,9,Frights of those living in the OPT, in
OL,10,Fwhich she and 30 other experts
OL,11,Fdescribed "genocide" as taking place
OL,12,Fin Gaza.
OL,14,FThe report, titled 'Genocide as
OL,15,Fcolonial erasure', also accused Israel
OL,16,Fof a "long-term intentional,
OL,17,Fsystematic, state-organised forced
OL,18,Fdisplacement and replacement of the
OL,19,FPalestinians".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
