OL,3,CUN human rights expert warns Israel is
OL,4,Cinflicting 'wanton destruction' on Gaza
OL,6,FIsrael has previously been accused by
OL,7,FSouth Africa of genocide in Gaza, with
OL,8,Fthe allegations brought before the
OL,9,FInternational Court of Justice (ICJ) -
OL,10,Fthe highest court in the UN.
OL,12,FThe case was originally launched in
OL,13,FDecember 2023, and 14 countries -
OL,14,Fincluding Spain, Belgium and the
OL,15,FRepublic of Ireland - have now
OL,16,Fannounced their intention to join it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
