OL,6,FMs Albanese said: "The other 30 UN
OL,7,Fexperts have called it a genocide.
OL,8,FIt's not only me, and there are
OL,9,Fhistorians and hundreds of legal
OL,10,Fexperts, including Israeli historians
OL,11,Fcovering genocide, talking about that.
OL,13,F"It's not only me but I'm the one who
OL,14,Fhas investigated for one year in
OL,15,Fdetail. So when I say genocide, is
OL,16,Fgenocide.
OL,18,FIsrael has accused the UN of bias, and
OL,19,Falleged Ms Albanese of being
OL,20,Fantisemitic - something she strongly
OL,21,Fdenies.
