OL,6,FMs Albanese, an Italian citizen, said
OL,7,Fshe was "horrified" by the collective
OL,8,FWestern reaction to events in the
OL,9,FMiddle East, and urged the United
OL,10,FStates to turn off the tap of military
OL,11,Fsupport to Israel.
OL,13,FShe said: "It has to happen now
OL,14,Fbecause it's 401 days too late
OL,15,Falready."
OL,17,FMs Albanese condemned Hamas' October 7
OL,18,Fattack, but added: "We shouldn't push
OL,19,Ffor this false equivalence between
OL,20,FIsrael and Hamas.
