OL,6,FThe last 24 hours marked the
OL,7,Fexpiration of a United States-set
OL,8,Fdeadline calling for Israel to "surge"
OL,9,Fgreater amounts of food and other
OL,10,Femergency aid into the territory or
OL,11,Frisk scaled-back American military
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,FUS officials had asked for a benchmark
OL,15,Fof 350 aid trucks each day, but
OL,16,Ffigures from the non-governmental
OL,17,Forganisation Refugees International
OL,18,Fshowed an average of 42 entered into
OL,19,FGaza, and that some days saw as few as
OL,20,Fsix.
