OL,6,FFrancesca Albanese told ITV News she
OL,7,Fbelieves there will be no
OL,8,F'significant' change in US-Israel
OL,9,Frelations despite limited progress on
OL,10,Fhumanitarian aid entering Gaza
OL,12,FAround 1,200 people died and some 250
OL,13,Fwere taken hostage on October 7 2023
OL,14,Fwhen Hamas militants attacked southern
OL,15,FIsrael.
OL,17,FMore than 40,000 Palestinians have
OL,18,Fsince died after the start of Israel's
OL,19,Fmilitary operation into the Gaza
OL,20,FStrip, according to the territory's
OL,21,FHamas-run Health Ministry.
