OL,6,FIsrael and its allies have repeatedly
OL,7,Fsaid it has a right to defend itself,
OL,8,Fbut Ms Albanese questioned whether the
OL,9,Floss of Israeli lives on October 7
OL,10,Fjustifies the "carnage", as she
OL,11,Fdescribed it, unfolding in Gaza.
OL,13,FShe said: "Is the killing of 1,000
OL,14,FIsraeli citizens, which includes 200
OL,15,For 300 military personnel, a
OL,16,Fjustification to carry out this
OL,17,Fcarnage?
