OL,6,F"The question is important because if
OL,7,Fthe answer is yes, I want to remind
OL,8,Fyou and those who are watching us at
OL,9,Fhome that just in the 16 years
OL,10,Fpreceding October 7, Israel had killed
OL,11,Fmore than 5,500 people, including
OL,12,F1,200 children."
OL,14,F'Is the killing of 1,000 Israeli
OL,15,Fcitizens a justification to carry out
OL,16,Fthis carnage?'
OL,18,FMs Albanese added: "We see Israel is
OL,19,Fburning people alive, is burning them
OL,20,Funder the rubble.
